# Voice Assistant

A simple voice assistant built with Python that can recognize voice commands, respond to basic queries, and open applications on your PC.

## Features

- Speech recognition
- Text-to-speech
- Basic commands (greetings, basic questions)
- Open applications (Notepad, Calculator, Chrome, Word, File Explorer, etc.)

## Requirements

- Python 3.x
- `SpeechRecognition` library
- `pyttsx3` library
- `pyaudio` library
